1
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:22,000
Mr. Zhen.

2
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:22,920
Young Master He.

3
00:00:22,920 --> 00:00:23,840
He Xiaochen.

4
00:00:23,840 --> 00:00:25,440
He admires the paintings

5
00:00:25,440 --> 00:00:26,640
you've discovered.

6
00:00:26,640 --> 00:00:27,800
He Art Museum

7
00:00:27,800 --> 00:00:28,560
wants to hold a joint exhibition

8
00:00:28,560 --> 00:00:29,800
with our gallery.

9
00:00:29,800 --> 00:00:30,720
I think

10
00:00:30,720 --> 00:00:32,640
this will greatly enhance the value

11
00:00:32,640 --> 00:00:33,880
of our gallery's collection

12
00:00:33,880 --> 00:00:34,960
and boost your prestige.

13
00:00:39,360 --> 00:00:41,040
If it's profitable,

14
00:00:41,040 --> 00:00:42,640
then go ahead.

15
00:00:44,040 --> 00:00:44,880
Yes.

16
00:00:44,880 --> 00:00:47,120
He Art Museum has a good reputation

17
00:00:47,120 --> 00:00:48,440
in the industry.

18
00:00:50,440 --> 00:00:51,360
But

19
00:00:51,360 --> 00:00:53,120
Young Master He said

20
00:00:53,120 --> 00:00:54,880
that he admires

21
00:00:54,880 --> 00:00:56,160
The Vanishing Rose the most.

22
00:00:58,160 --> 00:00:59,480
Does he want to borrow this one too?

23
00:01:00,640 --> 00:01:01,320
Yes.

24
00:01:01,320 --> 00:01:01,960
I know

25
00:01:01,960 --> 00:01:03,840
this is the most valuable work in the gallery.

26
00:01:03,840 --> 00:01:05,040
You value it highly.

27
00:01:05,040 --> 00:01:06,600
But Young Master He also said

28
00:01:06,600 --> 00:01:07,320
they would hire

29
00:01:07,320 --> 00:01:08,880
the highest level of security team

30
00:01:08,880 --> 00:01:10,080
and transportation team

31
00:01:10,080 --> 00:01:12,080
to ensure the safety of our work.

32
00:01:12,080 --> 00:01:13,400
Young Master He said...

33
00:01:13,400 --> 00:01:14,680
Young Master He said...

34
00:01:15,600 --> 00:01:16,680
Why do you listen to him for everything?

35
00:01:18,320 --> 00:01:20,160
Since he wants to hold the exhibition so much,

36
00:01:20,160 --> 00:01:21,800
let him talk to me first.

37
00:01:25,520 --> 00:01:26,720
President Zhen,

38
00:01:26,720 --> 00:01:28,080
I'll call him right now.

39
00:01:30,080 --> 00:01:30,480
President Zhen.

40
00:01:31,840 --> 00:01:32,280
President Zhen.

41
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:40,880
Hello, Mr. He.

42
00:01:40,880 --> 00:01:41,960
Hello, President Zhen.

43
00:01:41,960 --> 00:01:43,120
Regarding the joint exhibition,

44
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:44,400
have you decided?

45
00:01:45,080 --> 00:01:47,200
He Group's reputation is well-known in the industry.

46
00:01:47,200 --> 00:01:48,440
I have full confidence.

47
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:50,720
The exhibition details are complex.

48
00:01:50,720 --> 00:01:52,320
I'll have my curator

49
00:01:52,320 --> 00:01:53,320
communicate with Ms. Ye.

50
00:01:54,280 --> 00:01:54,840
By the way,

51
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:56,000
I'm also interested in

52
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:56,680
Ms. Ye's paintings.

53
00:01:57,080 --> 00:01:57,520
We can also

54
00:01:57,520 --> 00:01:59,360
include some of Ms. Ye's works

55
00:01:59,360 --> 00:02:00,360
in the exhibition.

56
00:02:01,440 --> 00:02:02,240
That's a good idea.

57
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:03,720
Good idea.

58
00:02:03,720 --> 00:02:04,440
I support it.

59
00:02:05,840 --> 00:02:06,120
Okay.

60
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:07,280
Mr. Zhen, sorry,

61
00:02:07,280 --> 00:02:09,000
I need to study my chess game.

62
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:10,280
Okay, go ahead.

63
00:02:10,639 --> 00:02:11,080
I'll have Zhiqiu

64
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:12,320
check the venue in a couple of days.

65
00:02:12,600 --> 00:02:13,360
No problem.

66
00:02:19,440 --> 00:02:20,320
[Judging from his reaction,]

67
00:02:20,320 --> 00:02:21,440
[Zhen Shida didn't suspect anything.]

68
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:23,120
[I can only say for now,]

69
00:02:25,600 --> 00:02:26,840
[play it by ear.]

70
00:02:27,640 --> 00:02:28,320
Mr. Zhen,

71
00:02:28,880 --> 00:02:29,760
you know,

72
00:02:29,760 --> 00:02:31,400
Mr. He,

73
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:33,480
comes from an artistic family.

74
00:02:33,480 --> 00:02:34,800
Don't mind him.

75
00:02:36,320 --> 00:02:38,400
What nonsense!

76
00:02:39,040 --> 00:02:41,160
It's like playing stocks.

77
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:43,880
The value of a work is determined by people.

78
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:45,520
Am I right,

79
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:46,200
Master Ye?

80
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:47,600
No.

81
00:02:47,600 --> 00:02:48,520
Your paintings

82
00:02:48,520 --> 00:02:49,720
were worthless before.

83
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:52,880
Now, with the help of my gallery,

84
00:02:52,880 --> 00:02:54,640
you've become a master.

85
00:02:58,040 --> 00:02:58,560
Listen up,

86
00:02:58,560 --> 00:02:59,360
Ye Zhiqiu.

87
00:02:59,960 --> 00:03:01,320
Hang your lousy paintings

88
00:03:01,320 --> 00:03:03,080
in the corner.

89
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:04,120
Did you hear me?

90
00:03:04,120 --> 00:03:05,240
Don't let me see them.

91
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:07,080
Don't drag down

92
00:03:07,080 --> 00:03:08,920
the overall level of the Era Gallery.

93
00:03:09,440 --> 00:03:10,400
You're right, Mr. Zhen.

94
00:03:11,760 --> 00:03:12,560
Mr. Zhen,

95
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:14,360
I will do my best

96
00:03:16,280 --> 00:03:17,720
to organize this exhibition.

97
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:21,560
Let's go.

98
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:43,320
Find me the contact information

99
00:03:43,320 --> 00:03:44,080
of Young Master He

100
00:03:44,080 --> 00:03:46,000
from the He Group.

101
00:03:56,360 --> 00:03:57,760
Ye Zhiqiu is calling.

102
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:03,960
Hello, Ms. Ye.

103
00:04:06,040 --> 00:04:07,080
What?

104
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:08,320
Now?

105
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:11,080
No problem.

106
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:12,320
I'll be right there.

107
00:04:14,760 --> 00:04:15,560
What's up?

108
00:04:17,279 --> 00:04:18,519
Ye Zhiqiu wants to check out the He Art Museum.

109
00:04:18,519 --> 00:04:19,200
to check the venue.

110
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:21,760
Why is it so sudden?

111
00:04:22,320 --> 00:04:23,880
We need to call the extras over immediately.

112
00:04:24,280 --> 00:04:25,040
There's no time.

113
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:25,800
What should we do then?

114
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:28,440
Cooperate with me on site.

115
00:04:28,440 --> 00:04:29,400
Just improvise.

116
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:38,240
Be careful, Ms. Ye.

117
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:39,320
Okay.

118
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:42,080
I've reserved the best spots in the gallery

119
00:04:42,080 --> 00:04:43,520
for your works.

120
00:04:43,520 --> 00:04:45,600
But I'm afraid that if President Zhen finds out,

121
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:46,880
say something bad?

122
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:48,960
It's okay.

123
00:04:48,960 --> 00:04:50,080
He doesn't like

124
00:04:50,080 --> 00:04:51,400
coming to these events anyway.

125
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:54,040
I'm just worried that you'll become famous

126
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:55,560
and it won't be possible to hide it.

127
00:04:57,960 --> 00:05:00,000
Being a painter has always been my dream.

128
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:01,400
If I can take this opportunity

129
00:05:01,400 --> 00:05:02,880
to gain recognition in the industry,

130
00:05:03,880 --> 00:05:04,600
I don't need

131
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:05,640
that job anymore.

132
00:05:05,640 --> 00:05:07,360
You should really thank me.

133
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:08,120
I've been

134
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:08,560
working non-stop

135
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:10,720
with Young Master He for you.

136
00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:13,240
I will.

137
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:16,320
Ms. Ye,

138
00:05:16,320 --> 00:05:16,920
look,

139
00:05:19,400 --> 00:05:21,120
the golden intersection of the traffic flow.

140
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:23,440
Checking the venue again?

141
00:05:23,440 --> 00:05:24,960
So many special exhibitions lately.

142
00:05:24,960 --> 00:05:26,720
If you put your "Erosion" series here

143
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:27,960
to dialogue

144
00:05:27,960 --> 00:05:29,560
with the peony series,

145
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:31,520
it would be a real hit.

146
00:05:35,760 --> 00:05:36,760
That's a good idea.

147
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:46,840
Excuse me for a moment.

148
00:05:47,640 --> 00:05:48,120
I'll go handle something first.

149
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:49,160
Alright, go ahead.

150
00:05:49,160 --> 00:05:49,720
Please take a look.

151
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:53,640
Thank you.

152
00:05:54,160 --> 00:05:55,520
Mr. Zhang is on a business trip.

153
00:05:55,520 --> 00:05:56,960
Could you go to his office

154
00:05:56,960 --> 00:05:58,960
and get the equipment passage documents?

155
00:05:58,960 --> 00:06:01,200
They're in the third drawer.

156
00:06:01,200 --> 00:06:02,000
Sure.

157
00:06:03,840 --> 00:06:04,640
Forester Lin,

158
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:06,720
thank you.

159
00:06:07,480 --> 00:06:08,600
Take a look here.

160
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:09,840
Let me tell you about the problem.

161
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:12,280
The angle of the basic spotlights

162
00:06:12,280 --> 00:06:13,800
in this reserved area

163
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:14,880
needs to be adjusted.

164
00:06:14,880 --> 00:06:16,200
This is too stiff,

165
00:06:16,200 --> 00:06:17,800
especially the light and shadow layers

166
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:19,160
of the core exhibit positions.

167
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:20,960
This is where the masterpieces will be placed.

168
00:06:21,640 --> 00:06:22,320
Okay.

169
00:06:22,320 --> 00:06:22,800
Okay.

170
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:27,320
James,

171
00:06:27,320 --> 00:06:28,200
you're right.

172
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:30,520
This is the core area.

173
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:36,440
Excuse me.

174
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:39,560
Mr. Ye,

175
00:06:40,080 --> 00:06:41,280
let's take a look at that painting.

176
00:06:42,080 --> 00:06:42,640
Okay.

177
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:47,400
Thank you.

178
00:06:47,400 --> 00:06:47,960
It's okay.

179
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:51,480
Sorry about that.

180
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:53,120
Let's continue over here.

181
00:06:54,560 --> 00:06:55,720
Thank you, James.

182
00:06:57,320 --> 00:06:58,000
Well,

183
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:59,280
it's about time.

184
00:06:59,280 --> 00:07:00,320
I'll go to the bathroom.

185
00:07:00,320 --> 00:07:00,840
After that,

186
00:07:00,840 --> 00:07:01,720
let's go back together.

187
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:02,560
Okay.

188
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:16,240
Excuse me,

189
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:17,920
may I ask

190
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:19,440
when the special exhibition

191
00:07:19,440 --> 00:07:20,640
of Era Gallery here

192
00:07:20,640 --> 00:07:21,800
will be opened?

193
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:22,640
What exhibition?
